---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/Layout.astro';
import TerminalWindow from '@components/TerminalWindow.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About | Genix">
  <TerminalWindow command="cat about.md">
    <div class="space-y-10">
      {/* Header */}
      <div class="space-y-4 pb-8 border-b border-gray-800">
        <h1 class="text-2xl text-white font-bold">Genix</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-300 text-base leading-relaxed">
          I build systems that trade simplicity for scale, and question abstractions until they fall apart.
          Most of my work lives somewhere between distributed messaging, event-driven architectures, and the philosophy of arrays.
          I like tools that do one thing well ‚Äî and refuse to quit.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm italic">
          Still learning. Still breaking my own designs.
        </p>
      </div>

      {/* Stack */}
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-gray-600">‚ñ∂</span>
          <h2 class="text-gray-300 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider font-bold">Stack</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <h3 class="text-white text-base font-semibold">Daily</h3>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="text-sm text-gray-300 bg-gray-900/50 px-3 py-1.5 rounded border border-gray-800">TypeScript</span>
              <span class="text-sm text-gray-300 bg-gray-900/50 px-3 py-1.5 rounded border border-gray-800">Node.js</span>
              <span class="text-sm text-gray-300 bg-gray-900/50 px-3 py-1.5 rounded border border-gray-800">Bun</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <h3 class="text-white text-base font-semibold">Data</h3>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="text-sm text-gray-300 bg-gray-900/50 px-3 py-1.5 rounded border border-gray-800">PostgreSQL</span>
              <span class="text-sm text-gray-300 bg-gray-900/50 px-3 py-1.5 rounded border border-gray-800">MongoDB</span>
              <span class="text-sm text-gray-300 bg-gray-900/50 px-3 py-1.5 rounded border border-gray-800">Redis</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <h3 class="text-white text-base font-semibold">Systems</h3>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="text-sm text-gray-300 bg-gray-900/50 px-3 py-1.5 rounded border border-gray-800">Linux</span>
              <span class="text-sm text-gray-300 bg-gray-900/50 px-3 py-1.5 rounded border border-gray-800">Docker</span>
              <span class="text-sm text-gray-300 bg-gray-900/50 px-3 py-1.5 rounded border border-gray-800">i3wm</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <h3 class="text-white text-base font-semibold">Editor</h3>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="text-sm text-gray-300 bg-gray-900/50 px-3 py-1.5 rounded border border-gray-800">Vim</span>
              <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 bg-gray-900/30 px-2 py-1 rounded">VEX config</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* Current Focus */}
      <div class="space-y-4 pb-8 border-b border-gray-800">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-gray-600">‚ñ∂</span>
          <h2 class="text-gray-300 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider font-bold">Currently</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-green-400 text-sm mt-1">‚óè</span>
            <div>
              <div class="text-gray-200 text-base">Writing ARLIZ</div>
              <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-1">
                A book exploring data structures from their historical origins
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-green-400 text-sm mt-1">‚óè</span>
            <div>
              <div class="text-gray-200 text-base">Building GLAND</div>
              <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-1">
                An event-driven architecture for JavaScript systems
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-yellow-400 text-sm mt-1">‚óê</span>
            <div>
              <div class="text-gray-200 text-base">Studying Algorithm Analysis</div>
              <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-1">
                Deepening understanding of complexity theory and formal methods
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* Philosophy */}
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-gray-600">‚ñ∂</span>
          <h2 class="text-gray-300 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider font-bold">Philosophy</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-300 text-base leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            I'm fascinated by the intersection of philosophy and computation.
            How do we know what we know? What makes a proof convincing?
            Why do abstractions work‚Äîuntil they don't?
          </p>
          <p>
            Writing is thinking. That's why I write books, articles, and documentation.
            Not to teach‚Äîto learn. Every explanation forces clarity. Every attempt to
            simplify reveals what I don't understand.
          </p>
          <p>
            Systems over solutions. How components interact matters more than what they do
            individually. Emergence is more interesting than implementation. Architecture
            outlasts code.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* Random Facts */}
      <div class="space-y-4 pb-8 border-b border-gray-800">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-gray-600">‚ñ∂</span>
          <h2 class="text-gray-300 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider font-bold">Random</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-gray-500 mt-0.5">‚Üí</span>
            <span class="text-gray-300">I've read more about data structures than implemented them</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-gray-500 mt-0.5">‚Üí</span>
            <span class="text-gray-300">My GitHub contributions look like a heartbeat monitor</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-gray-500 mt-0.5">‚Üí</span>
            <span class="text-gray-300">I debug by writing‚Äîif I can't explain it, I don't understand it</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-gray-500 mt-0.5">‚Üí</span>
            <span class="text-gray-300">Terminal first, GUI second (or never)</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* Contact */}
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-gray-600">‚ñ∂</span>
          <h2 class="text-gray-300 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider font-bold">Contact</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="text-gray-500 text-lg">üì¨</span>
            <a href="mailto:bitsgenix@gmail.com" 
               class="text-gray-300 hover:text-white transition-colors">
              bitsgenix@gmail.com
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="text-gray-500 text-lg">üêô</span>
            <a href="https://github.com/m-mdy-m" 
               target="_blank" 
               rel="noopener noreferrer"
               class="text-gray-300 hover:text-white transition-colors">
              github.com/m-mdy-m
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="text-gray-500 text-lg">üìù</span>
            <a href="https://dev.to/m__mdy__m" 
               target="_blank" 
               rel="noopener noreferrer"
               class="text-gray-300 hover:text-white transition-colors">
              dev.to/m__mdy__m
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* Footer */}
      <div class="pt-6 border-t border-gray-800">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 text-xs">
          <a href="/articles" class="text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-300 transition-colors">
            [articles]
          </a>
          <a href="/thoughts" class="text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-300 transition-colors">
            [thoughts]
          </a>
          <a href="/projects" class="text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-300 transition-colors">
            [projects]
          </a>
          <a href="/books" class="text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-300 transition-colors">
            [books]
          </a>
          <a href="/contact" class="text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-300 transition-colors">
            [contact]
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </TerminalWindow>
</BaseLayout>